{"tid":2173824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最新民研電話調查顯示林鄭評分及支持都破一年新高 ,  不過網上評分係負420分","createTime":"2020-08-25T12:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T13:10:35.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9de4f964bbba398025803a1cdf4d6983ab1fd6","tid":2173824,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:53:22.000Z","msg":"香港民意研究計劃最新調查顯示，行政長官林鄭月娥的評分為 26.8 分，有 53% 受訪者給予林鄭 0 分，評分與半個月前分別不大。林鄭的支持率為 24%，較半個月前升 5 個百分點，民望淨值為負 46 個百分點，較半個月前升 8 個百分點，兩者都創下去年七月以來的新高。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提是民研計劃以不同差距的量表，讓參與網上問卷的市民評分，即分別是負 50 至 50 分、負 100 至 100 分以及負 1,000 至 1,000 分為林鄭評分。這項調查接到逾 2.8 萬份回應，結果顯示當有負數選項時，林鄭月娥在這三項量表的評分全為負數，分別是負 19.1、負 40.6 及 負 420.3。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%8E%87%E5%89%B5%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-1000-%E5%88%86%E6%BB%BF%E5%88%86%E7%8D%B2%E8%A9%95%E8%B2%A0-420-%E5%88%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%258E%2587%25E5%2589%25B5%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598-1000-%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%258D%25B2%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25B2%25A0-420-%25E5%2588%2586%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=ee00352c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%258E%2587%25E5%2589%25B5%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598-1000-%25E5%2588%2586%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%258D%25B2%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25B2%25A0-420-%25E5%2588%2586%2F&h=29104ee1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%8E%87%E5%89%B5%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-1000-%E5%88%86%E6%BB%BF%E5%88%86%E7%8D%B2%E8%A9%95%E8%B2%A0-420-%E5%88%86/</a>"},{"pid":"c350b30c577d5070ce6d385590246209fac7e289","tid":2173824,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:54:54.000Z","msg":"負分呢個系統幾好"},{"pid":"4fcfb962923e02205a2cf4269528123bd114e722","tid":2173824,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:56:40.000Z","msg":"牙娥：我效忠維尼"},{"pid":"b49c690a34655e757347f785a3df856ea31e12da","tid":2173824,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:58:45.000Z","msg":"負咁撚多都仲可以做落去<br />\n係獨裁政權先得<br />\n獨裁者鄭月蛾<br />\n大獨裁者維尼熊"},{"pid":"54e0cb9c9890d1c03f5f88b841c3d3cd48272d76","tid":2173824,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:10:35.000Z","msg":"咁都唔過負500<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}